items.headline: Welcome to Paranormal Witness
items.desc: Time to scream, cry and fight back.  This site is about the show Paranormal Witness Series.  Currently the best Paranormal Show on TV.  Relive the events that make up the episodes.  See the creatures that go bump in the night.  Visit the places where fear has come to life.  Talk about the epiosdes that scared you or amazed you.  All is welcome, if you dare.
